and h1 : "\<forall> r. Q r = (r + 5) powr 2"
shows  "\<forall> r. P r = Q r"

 Factor $r^2+10r+25$. The final Answer is (r+5)^2
 ### Proof

 *)

shows  "\<forall> r. P r = Q r"
 proof- 
  show ?thesis sledgehammer
